#40102
A Path In The Village of the Troffs~
You are on a well worn path in the small, busy village of the Troffs. The air
is fragrant with the smell of grass and tree's. Its a warm summers day and the
Troff's are out and about. The occasional Troff smiles at you or waves, but you
are left alone by them. The path contines to the north where you can see 
several mud huts.
