#40103
The Village of the Troff's~
The path is getting a little wider and you are getting bumped occasionally by
Troffs busy transporting farm produce and simple tools to the local market. 
Some Troffs are just sitting down by the side of the road soaking in the sun. 
It looks good to be a Troff. To the east is a mud house with a large white 
square above the door. To the west is a slightly larger house with a slightly 
larger yellow square. The path also continues to the north and the south.
