#40104
The Village of the Troff's~
You're standing on the dirt path with the bustle of Troff's all around you.
In the distance to the north you can see some fields. But you're a bit to far
away to see exactly what's going on in them. To the east is a mud house with
a green square on the front of it. To the west is a mud house with a blue 
square on it. You feel pretty sure these different colours you've been seeing 
have something to do with how tough the clan that lives in these houses are.
The dirt path continues to the north and south.
