#40105
The Village of the Troff's near the Fields~
Here the path takes a turn to the east. To the north and west you can see 
wide open fields. You think you can make out some odd creatures in the 
distance, but you're a bit too far away. Looking south you can see the path 
continue, and you can make out two mud houses.
