#40106
The Village of the Troff's~
To your north is a rather large mud house with a large red square attached
to the front. The house looks a bit more ornate and you can see a few 
practice swords leaning up against the wall. The path continues to the east 
and west. In The far east you can see two more large, ornate mud houses. 
The path is not nearly so busy and you start to feel a touch nervous.
