#40107
The Village of the Troff's~
To your south is an ornate mud house. It is festooned with brown banners
and has a large brown square placed above the door. You can see Troff's 
outside practicing with live blades and moving very skillfully. You're 
just about positive they're not farmers. To the east is a massive mud hut 
painted black. There is no ornamentation and nobody is outside. The small 
path leading to the house is clean and narrow. You notice how the Troff's 
practicing infront of the the brown house are careful not to get too close
to the black house.
