#40108
Entry Hall of the White Clan's House~
You enter a small hall in this modest mud brick home. Around the walls are
assorted farming implements. They look well used and well
maintained. The floor is dirt and well worn and sun streams in through
the windows. This is a comfortable place for the White Troff's.
